data.text: The Kern County Superintendent of Schools Educational Services Foundation is the proud recipient of an Outdoor Equity Grant in partnership with Children First in East Bakersfield. This program is funded by the Outdoor Equity Grants Program, created through AB 209 and administered by California State Parks, Office of Grants and Local Services.
